{
  "stem": "17135.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when-- when you were-- were-- were asked by an SS officer, you had to say, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had no name anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were only numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- you had immediately to report to him who you are.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the rule.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You are just a number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- it's like, like when you get a-- a-- a-- an injection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's really done by injection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it's a needle and they're points, you saw this, didn't you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was done by Polish-- by Polish prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, there were lots of Polish prisoners-- political prisoners-- in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, they were all deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- only Jews stayed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told us, please, don't pretend it hurts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You haven't-- you don't even know what hurts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You will find out what hurt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That is-- that is peanuts, so to speak, he told us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He prepared us all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were very cynical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- interesting enough, the Polish prisoners, although some of them were communists and socialists, they hated the Nazis and hated the Jews at the same time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Not all of them, but I feel the majority.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I will tell you when we came to-- to-- to Auschwitz, the Polish kapos, how they behaved.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we're going to get to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So anyway, that was our arrival in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- they told us right there, if you get a number, you are destined to work-- to work yourself to death, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they threw us in the shower-- cold shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was October.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was icy cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
